Setup instructions are really confusing and scattered everywhere. We should resolve that as a documentation problem, and as a `Makefile` problem. I've attempted to do both here by making requirements more explicit in some cases, and wherever possible failing early in the `Makefile` if some necessary dependency isn't installed. 

Motivated by @sashamitelman's trouble running `make` this afternoon.

